OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,FDuring two phone conversations from
OL,7,FTehran's notorious Evin prison, the 53-
OL,8,Fyear-old from East Sussex told Global
OL,9,FSecurity Editor Rohit Kachroo of her
OL,10,Ftime in solitary confinement.
OL,12,FShe spoke of the psychological torture
OL,13,Fof being imprisoned near her husband
OL,14,Fbut with only occasional contact, the
OL,15,F"multiple times" she has been told she
OL,16,Fwas being released - and the
OL,17,F"depressing" realisation it wasn't
OL,18,Fgoing to happen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
