OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,FLindsay and her husband Craig were
OL,7,Ftaken into custody during a motorcycle
OL,8,Ftour around the world in January 2025
OL,9,F- they were charged with espionage a
OL,10,Fmonth later.
OL,12,FThe couple have been imprisoned ever
OL,13,Fsince, and deny all charges against
OL,14,Fthem. They are being held in the same
OL,15,Fprison where Nazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe
OL,16,Fwas held.
OL,18,F"If I could do anything to change the
OL,19,Fsituation here, I will do it, even if
OL,20,FI'm at risk," Lindsay said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
