OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,F"So having this call, they are
OL,7,Frecorded ... And there's a risk that I
OL,8,Fwill have my calls cut, I'll be put in
OL,9,Fsolitary confinement, I'll have
OL,10,Fanother file open on me. But I have to
OL,11,Fdo something. I can't sit and do
OL,12,Fnothing."
OL,14,FLindsay shared her experience of her
OL,15,Ftime spent in "solitary confinement",
OL,16,Fwhich she described as "a massive
OL,17,Fmental test".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
