OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,F"The emotions are extreme. You know,
OL,7,Fthe lows are really low and the highs
OL,8,Fwhen people get released ... You know
OL,9,F(it) is a bit of a journey."
OL,11,FOn her false hopes of being released,
OL,12,Fshe said: "Literally, they've said the
OL,13,Fwords: 'You're going to be released
OL,14,Fnext week, you're going to be' - you
OL,15,Fknow, even when they transported us
OL,16,Ffrom Kerman (a city in the south-east)
OL,17,Fto Tehran, we were on a commercial
OL,18,Fflight, we were wearing our own
OL,19,Fclothes, you know, there were no
OL,20,Fhandcuffs, no blindfolds.
