OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,F"We knew it was going to Tehran, but
OL,7,Feverybody, the guards at the Kerman
OL,8,Fprison, you know, said that this is,
OL,9,Fyou know, this is release. The
OL,10,Fprosecutor that we'd had there said
OL,11,Fyou'd be going to Tehran and onto the
OL,12,FUK."
OL,14,FBut Lindsay and her husband were no
OL,15,Fcloser to going home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
