OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,F"But not only was it not the end, the
OL,7,Fprogress we thought we'd made in
OL,8,FKerman with getting a lawyer,
OL,9,Feventually, you know, being told we
OL,10,Fwere going to court, all just stopped
OL,11,Fand we ended up going back and having
OL,12,Fto start again.
OL,14,F"(The most) pitiful, depressing
OL,15,Fmoment, I think I've ever experienced
OL,16,Fthat actual belief that this is the
OL,17,Fend, only for it all to start,
OL,18,Fliterally all start all over again,"
OL,19,Fshe added.
