OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,FLindsay said she is able to see her
OL,7,Fhusband Craig, who is also detained in
OL,8,FEvin prison, but described the
OL,9,Fmeetings as "psychological torture".
OL,11,F"So for example, we were promised
OL,12,Fthree meetings a month, which can
OL,13,Frange between, I think the (shortest)
OL,14,Fhas been about 45 minutes ... and the
OL,15,Flongest I think we've had is about,
OL,16,Fyou know, just over two hours."
OL,18,F"On more than one occasion, they
OL,19,Fcancel it at the last minute. And that
OL,20,Fis the most soul-destroying thing."
