OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,FLindsay spoke about people she has met
OL,7,Fin the prison, including those
OL,8,Farrested during recent protests in
OL,9,FIran.
OL,11,F"There's a young girl who came in...
OL,12,Fshe's been sentenced to 25 years for
OL,13,Fprotesting last month. And her dad who
OL,14,Fwas also protesting with her has been
OL,15,Fsentenced to death.
OL,17,FDescribing how she tries to offer
OL,18,Fcomfort, she said: "Well I can't speak
OL,19,Fbecause we are limited by language, I
OL,20,Fdo what I can to make them feel better
OL,21,Fthrough breath and through hugs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
