OL,6,F"If I can help them with that through
OL,7,Fa hug or through, you know, sharing
OL,8,Fwhat's happening here, then yeah, it
OL,9,Fwill be worth it."
OL,11,F'There's a risk of detainment, but how
OL,12,Fbad can that be?'
OL,14,FLindsay said she and Craig have been
OL,15,Ftold they were "spies" and that they
OL,16,Fwere "working with Israel" as an
OL,17,Fexplanation for them being detained.
