OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,FThe couple were originally heading for
OL,7,FAustralia, having crossed into Iran
OL,8,Ffrom Armenia on December 30, 2024,
OL,9,Faccording to social media posts
OL,10,Fdocumenting their travels.
OL,12,FLindsay was carrying out a research
OL,13,Fproject as part of the original
OL,14,Fjourney, asking people what
OL,15,Fconstitutes a "good life".
OL,17,FShe has since been adding paper
OL,18,Fmessages to that project from the
OL,19,Fprisoners in Evin, posting them on a
OL,20,Fwall in the corridor where inmates
OL,21,Fmake their phone calls.
