OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,F"One of the first ones I can see is
OL,7,F'every day renew your love'. So going
OL,8,Fdown a very grey grim wall is a multi
OL,9,Fcoloured rainbow of messages of hope.
OL,10,FSo I get to look at that when I'm on
OL,11,Fthe phone, which is nice," she said.
OL,13,FLindsay also explained the couple had
OL,14,Ftravelled through Iran, despite
OL,15,FForeign Office warnings to not enter
OL,16,Fthe country, because of logistics, and
OL,17,Fthat they believed they had the
OL,18,Fcorrect documentation to be there.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
