OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,F"When you're planning a route around
OL,7,Fthe world, it's quite complicated, and
OL,8,FIran is a big section of that, you
OL,9,Fknow, gateway from Europe to Asia ...
OL,10,FI thought getting a visa was a sign of
OL,11,Fa welcome.
OL,13,F"Armenia was having a storm, Turkey
OL,14,Fwas having a snowstorm. So had I known
OL,15,Fthat, I probably would have gone a
OL,16,Fsafer political route, whilst more
OL,17,Fdangerous geographically.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
