OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,F"We had an Iranian travel agent
OL,7,Fplotting our routes. We had a tour
OL,8,Fguide. We were escorted. I think the
OL,9,Fpeople who told us, you know, you,
OL,10,F'this is possible, you can do it.'
OL,12,F"We kind of felt ... There's a risk of
OL,13,Fdetainment, but how bad can that be?
OL,14,FHow, you know, if we're innocent
OL,15,Fpeople, why would they detain us? So I
OL,16,Fnaively and ignorantly thought that
OL,17,Fwe'd be okay."
OL,19,FThe couple had posted about the risks
OL,20,Fof being in Iran when they first
OL,21,Farrived in the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
