OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,F"To put your minds at rest, we are
OL,7,Fhaving the most amazing time in Iran,"
OL,8,Fthey wrote on Facebook on January 3,
OL,9,Fshortly before they were arrested.
OL,11,FIn another post on Instagram, Lindsay
OL,12,Fdid acknowledge that travelling to
OL,13,FIran, against Foreign Office advice,
OL,14,Fwas "slightly scary".
OL,16,F"Yes, we're aware of the risks. But we
OL,17,Falso know the rewards of meeting
OL,18,Fincredible people, hearing their
OL,19,Fstories, and seeing the breathtaking
OL,20,Flandscapes of these regions could far
OL,21,Foutweigh the fear."
