OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,FA Foreign Office spokesperson told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "We remain deeply concerned that
OL,8,FCraig and Lindsay Foreman have been
OL,9,Fcharged with espionage in Iran. We
OL,10,Fcontinue to raise this case directly
OL,11,Fwith the Iranian authorities.
OL,13,F"We continue to provide Craig and
OL,14,FLindsay with consular assistance and
OL,15,Fremain in close contact with their
OL,16,Ffamily members."
OL,18,FLindsay's son Joe handed a petition to
OL,19,FDowning Street in early January this
OL,20,Fyear, calling on the government to do
OL,21,Fmore to free the couple.
