OL,3,CBritish mum Lindsay Foreman speaks out
OL,4,Cfrom Iran's notorious Evin prison
OL,6,FJoe Bennett was joined by former
OL,7,Fdetainee Anoosheh Ashoori and Richard
OL,8,FRatcliffe, who fought a public
OL,9,Fcampaign that involved two hunger
OL,10,Fstrikes to have his wife Nazanin
OL,11,FZaghari-Ratcliffe freed from Iran, at
OL,12,Fthe steps of Number 10 to deliver the
OL,13,F70,000-signature petition.
OL,15,F"We want public acknowledgement that
OL,16,Fit is completely barbaric they are
OL,17,Fbeing held on these charges of
OL,18,Fespionage, that they are not spies for
OL,19,Fthe British state and they are going
OL,20,Fto do everything they can to get them
OL,21,Fhome," he said in January.
